	/// Tableau 'IF [Latest Steps Count] > [Prior Steps Count] THEN [Latest Steps Count] - [Prior Steps Count] END' (positive-change branch; BLANK otherwise).
	measure 'Steps Count Diff +' = VAR _l = [Latest Steps Count] VAR _p = [Prior Steps Count] RETURN IF(_l > _p, _l - _p)
		formatString: #,##0.0
		displayFolder: Diff (Latest vs Prior)
		lineageTag: ba215aaf-2e5d-4b0a-b3db-ef00f7106c9d

	/// Tableau 'IF [Latest Steps Count] < [Prior Steps Count] THEN [Latest Steps Count] - [Prior Steps Count] END' (negative-change branch; BLANK otherwise).
